text VyratonOutdoors_Harbour_Text_WelcomeToVyraton
{
    format("
        Hello there, you must be {PLAYER}!\n
        Welcome to our humble town, Vyraton!\l
        I'm so very glad you're here.\p
        It's me, Samuel, we spoke earlier on.\n
        I'm the mayor around here.\p

        {SPEAKER_NAME NAME_AUTO}I can't tell you how much this town\n
        has been anticipating your arrival.\l
        Around here, things have been…\p
        Well, let's just say that we could most\n
        certainly use someone like you!\l
        Ah, but where are my manners?\p
        You've only just arrived and I'm\n
        already rambling, you must be tired.\l
        And we already have a lot to discuss…\p

        But before we make our way to my\n
        office, let's stay for the departure.\p
        The S.S. Pathfinder is meant to bring\n
        good luck to all who journey on it.\l
        And as always, it's truly majestic…")
}

text VyratonOutdoors_Harbour_Text_HeadToOffice
{
    format("
        I will never get bored of that view…\n
        {PAUSE 30}Come on, {PLAYER}. Let's head off.\p
        It's just a short walk, but we should\n
        make a move before it gets too late.")
}